snippet.textDisplay: The Roadmap for PS4 ->PS5 has come to an end. Is it the reason for the Car. Moors Law told us about the PS3/4 decades ago. Snes 3.5 mhz, PS1 33 Mhz, PS2 300Mhz. PS3 3.2 GHz. PS4 (Small improvement) as some workloads are moved to the secondary core (e.g Networking). The game engine isn't fully multi-threaded. If you don't know how to do multi-threading properly then it slows down instead of speeds up.
